BM   hmmbuild  -o /dev/null HMM SEED
SM   hmmsearch -Z 90746521 --cpu 8 -E 1000 HMM pfamseq
TP   Family
CC   This entry represents an N-terminal sensor domain (approximately
CC   60-234 residues) found in bacterial histidine kinases. This region
CC   precedes PAS domains and histidine kinase catalytic domains, and is
CC   involved in signal perception in two-component regulatory systems.
CC   The family is found in Pseudomonadota (Marinilabiliales,
CC   Rhodospirillales, Gammaproteobacteria, Alphaproteobacteria),
CC   Thermodesulfobacteriota and Bacteroidota.
